atus\":\"tombstone\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:21:14.717730563-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_by\":\"batch delete\",\"delete_reason\":\"batch delete\",\"original_type\":\"task\"}\n+{\"id\":\"cloche-r3b\",\"title\":\"Investigate cloche orchestrate 'No ready work found' despite open tasks\",\"description\":\"cloche orchestrate returns 'No ready work found' even though bd list shows 4 open, unblocked P2 tasks. The daemon-side orchestrator state may not be syncing with the beads tracker, or the concurrency setting (overridden to 1) may be causing unexpected behavior. Investigate the daemon-side orchestration registration, gRPC handler flow, and in-memory inFlight tracking.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-07T08:55:13.252440805-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T08:55:13.252440805-08:00\"}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-req\",\"title\":\"Implement per-project merge queue in orchestrator\",\"description\":\"Add a per-project FIFO merge queue to the orchestrator. When a run completes with 'done' result, enqueue its branch (cloche/\\u003crunID\\u003e) for merging. Each project processes one merge at a time. Different projects can merge in parallel. Queue state persisted in SQLite. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §1 Merge Queue.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"Successful runs enqueue for merge. Queue is per-project FIFO. Queue state persists across daemon restarts.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:00:36.498019112-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T15:40:57.581589902-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T15:40:57.581589902-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-req\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-2ju\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:01:15.385283535-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"title\":\"Subdirectory layout, daemon-side extraction, and poll command\",\"description\":\"Move cloche project files into ./cloche/ subdirectory, replace in-container git push with daemon-side extraction via docker cp + git worktrees, and add a poll CLI command. See docs/plans/2026-03-01-subdirectory-layout-and-poll-design.md and docs/plans/2026-03-01-subdirectory-layout-and-poll-impl.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"epic\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:36.813893794-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:20:53.846404063-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T17:20:53.846406999-08:00\"}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.1\",\"title\":\"Add BaseSHA field to domain and persistence\",\"description\":\"Add BaseSHA string field to domain.Run struct. Add ALTER TABLE migration for base_sha column in SQLite. Update CreateRun, GetRun, ListRuns, ListRunsSince to persist/read BaseSHA.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:42.907595121-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T15:39:47.752780627-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T15:39:47.752783963-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.1\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:51:42.909407284-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n@@ -99,7 +100,7 @@\n {\"id\":\"cloche-rxi.9\",\"title\":\"Add container_alive and container_dead_since to proto\",\"description\":\"Add bool container_alive (field 8) and string container_dead_since (field 9) to GetStatusResponse in cloche.proto. Regenerate gRPC code.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":10,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:28.835726418-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T16:54:06.402271696-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-01T16:54:06.402274461-08:00\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.9\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"type\":\"parent-child\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:28.836804384-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-rxi.9\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-rxi.1\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T14:52:28.838661512-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-s1j\",\"title\":\"Add dedicated /projects/{name} page\",\"description\":\"Create a dedicated project detail page at /projects/{name} with three panels: orchestrator control, project info, and workflow view. See docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-pages-design.md for full design.\",\"design\":\"docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-pages-design.md\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- /projects/{name} route exists and renders\\n- Project cards on landing page link to /projects/{name}\\n- Orchestrator panel shows enabled/disabled status, in-flight count, concurrency; toggle and override work\\n- Project info panel shows docker image, version, prompt file git history with diff on click\\n- Workflow view renders steps and wires as a DAG; clicking a step opens a drawer with prompt/script content\\n- New API endpoints: GET/POST /api/projects/{name}/orchestrator, GET /api/projects/{name}/info, GET /api/projects/{name}/workflows\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:25:03.347821436-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T18:25:01.972742703-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T18:25:01.972742703-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-s1j\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-8zs\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:48.130988517-08:00\",\"created_by\":