ying binaries. Cover approaches like go install, pre-built release binaries, Homebrew tap, Docker-based usage, and any other practical distribution methods.\",\"status\":\"in_progress\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-27T12:35:01.057514125-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T13:19:34.131667749-08:00\"}\n+{\"id\":\"cloche-cxs\",\"title\":\"Document Cloche installation options\",\"description\":\"Document options for installing Cloche on other machines beyond manually copying binaries. Cover approaches like go install, pre-built release binaries, Homebrew tap, Docker-based usage, and any other practical distribution methods.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-27T12:35:01.057514125-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T08:51:40.479896112-08:00\"}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-d3p\",\"title\":\"Wire capture through runner to status protocol\",\"description\":\"Connect prompt adapter OnCapture to StatusWriter in runner. Emit new status messages with prompt/output data. See Task 6 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":20,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:35.279067432-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:41:50.456338633-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:41:50.456338633-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-d3p\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-aw5\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.709590864-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-dzz\",\"title\":\"Add host.cloche and workflow step type for orchestrator\",\"description\":\"Add a host.cloche DSL file that defines an 'orchestrate' workflow running on the host mach