d_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:41:50.529265221-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:41:50.529265221-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-osk\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-0aa\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.884318161-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-pik\",\"title\":\"Add health API endpoint and cloche health CLI command\",\"description\":\"Extend GET /api/projects to include health field per project. Add cloche health CLI command showing table of all projects with health status and passed/failed counts. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §2.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"API returns health data. CLI displays health table.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:42:04.620982239-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.713343966-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.713343966-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-pik\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-3ic\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:45:38.457553706-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-q6n\",\"title\":\"Update Run model for concurrent steps\",\"description\":\"- type: task\",\"status\":\"tombstone\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:21:14.717730563-08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_at\":\"2026-02-20T20:23:00.287387199-08:00\",\"deleted_by\":\"batch delete\",\"delete_reason\":\"batch delete\",\"original_type\":\"task\"}\n+{\"id\":\"cloche-r3b\",\"title\":\"Investigate cloche orchestrate 'No ready work found' despite open tasks\",\"description\":\"cloche orchestrate returns 'No ready work found' even though bd list shows 4 open, unblocked P2 tasks. The daemon-side orchestrator state may not be syncing with the beads tracker, or the concurrency setting (overridden to 1) may be causing unexpected behavior. Investigate the daemon-side orchestration registration, gRPC handler flow, and in-memory inFlight tracking.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-07T08:55:13.252440805-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T08:55:13.252440805-08:00\"}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-req\",\"title\":\"Implement per-project merge queue in orchestrator\",\"description\":\"Add a per-project FIFO merge queue to the orchestrator. When a run completes with 'done' result, enqueue its branch (cloche/\\u003crunID\\u003e) for merging. Each project processes one merge at a time. Different projects can merge in parallel. Queue state persisted in SQLite. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §1 Merge Queue.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"Successful runs enqueue for merge. Queue is per-project FIFO. Queue state persists across daemon restarts.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:00:36.498019112-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T15:40:57.581589902-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T15:40:57.581589902-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-req\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-2ju\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T11:01:15.385283535-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-rxi\",\"title\":\"Subdirectory layout, daemon-side extraction, and poll command\",\"description\":\"Move cloche project files into ./cloche/ subdirectory, replace in-container git push with daemon-side extraction via docker cp + git worktrees, and add a poll CLI command. See docs/plans/2026-03-01-subdirectory-layout-and-poll-design.md and docs/plans/2026-03-01-subdirectory-layout-and-poll-impl.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"epic\",\"owner\":\"l