ojects/{name} page\",\"description\":\"Create a dedicated project detail page at /projects/{name} with three panels: orchestrator control, project info, and workflow view. See docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-pages-design.md for full design.\",\"design\":\"docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-pages-design.md\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- /projects/{name} route exists and renders\\n- Project cards on landing page link to /projects/{name}\\n- Orchestrator panel shows enabled/disabled status, in-flight count, concurrency; toggle and override work\\n- Project info panel shows docker image, version, prompt file git history with diff on click\\n- Workflow view renders steps and wires as a DAG; clicking a step opens a drawer with prompt/script content\\n- New API endpoints: GET/POST /api/projects/{name}/orchestrator, GET /api/projects/{name}/info, GET /api/projects/{name}/workflows\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:25:03.347821436-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T18:25:01.972742703-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T18:25:01.972742703-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-s1j\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-8zs\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:48.130988517-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-sdc\",\"title\":\"EvolutionStore port and SQLite implementation\",\"description\":\"Define EvolutionStore interface (SaveEvolution, GetLastEvolution, ListRunsSince) and implement on SQLite Store. See Task 3 in docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":20,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:07:35.154118688-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:28:13.006092287-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:28:13.006092287-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"evolution\"],\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-sdc\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-myv\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-24T10:09:29.60418848-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n-{\"id\":\"cloche-t62\",\"title\":\"Auto-rebuild stale containers on cloche run\",\"description\":\"Validate that the container image is up-to-date before launching a workflow run. If the project Dockerfile or base image has changed since the last build, rebuild automatically so the container runs the correct cloche-agent and dependencies. This check should happen in the daemon when processing a RunWorkflow request.\",\"status\":\"in_progress\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-27T12:34:59.78809366-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:03:57.961057724-08:00\"}\n+{\"id\":\"cloche-t62\",\"title\":\"Auto-rebuild stale containers on cloche run\",\"description\":\"Validate that the container image is up-to-date before launching a workflow run. If the project Dockerfile or base image has changed since the last build, rebuild automatically so the container runs the correct cloche-agent and dependencies. This check should happen in the daemon when processing a RunWorkflow request.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-27T12:34:59.78809366-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T08:51:40.438970384-08:00\"}\n {\"id\":\"cloche-toz\",\"title\":\"Implement container retention policy for failed runs\",\"description\":\"Change container lifecycle so failed runs automatically keep their container for debugging. Successful runs continue to auto-delete. Preserve --keep-container flag for keeping containers regardless of outcome. Track retained containers in SQLite (container ID, run ID, project, creation time, status). See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §5.\",